                <note rend="inline" type="source">511.3B1/5a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-10-02T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 2, 1919—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3310. Can you inform Department of any reason why Brazil is not signatory of the
                    Arms Traffic Convention?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
